# Template URLs — not meant to resolve until the referenced infra is created.
# Each regex is matched against the full URL; one per line.
# Remove entries as the underlying targets are created.

# Phase 15 will create the `forge-reference-deployments` GitHub org. Until
# then, URLs like `https://github.com/forge-reference-deployments/<lib-name>`
# (lychee strips the `<lib-name>` placeholder and tries to resolve the org
# root, which 404s) are template placeholders in plan docs, not real links.
^https://github\.com/forge-reference-deployments/.*$
